{"tid":982943,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[F4要入MCU？]蟻俠導演派頓·瑞德講述自己未拍成的神奇四俠電影概念與劇情","createTime":"2019-01-15T14:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T04:24:36.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffbd9d05f4ac4168e0ae6b847a43e46e9d9f333","tid":982943,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=5615&amp;fbclid=IwAR2lLse2ztRqklXUkZ29tetWyjUti4uzhia_SYOcNp49W58WHy3JNfs1cMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgeek-base.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D5615%26fbclid%3DIwAR2lLse2ztRqklXUkZ29tetWyjUti4uzhia_SYOcNp49W58WHy3JNfs1cMI&d=tZkk7dfkwHAvYrzRQcIe%2F5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=fd6a1e0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://geek-base.toy-people.com/?p=5615&amp;fbclid=IwAR2lLse2ztRqklXUkZ29tetWyjUti4uzhia_SYOcNp49W58WHy3JNfs1cMI</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/154754529541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F154754529541.jpg&h=f30c4634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今天 Collider 透過 Comic Book 公開的訪問中，《蟻人和黃蜂女》導演派頓&middot;瑞德講述自己沒拍成的驚奇四超人電影構想，他提到這部作品跟前兩版福斯的電影走向和劇情會完全不同，而且非常接近早期漫畫的元素。<br />\n<br />\n派頓&middot;瑞德說道這部電影發展了一年多，中間有不少導演和編劇加入過，時間點會設定在 60 年代，跟驚奇四超人原作時剛出的年代類似，劇情風格會像披頭四主演的《一夜狂歡》（A Hard Day's Night），而且不會討論起源故事，他們四人組已經存在於曼哈頓許久，不過構想這計畫的時候是 2002、2003 年，也是 MCU 出現前的時代，福斯不喜歡這樣的計畫才導致作罷～<br />\n<br />\n附帶一提，派頓&middot;瑞德說道他認為兩版的驚奇四超人電影是俗氣的Ｂ級片，所以不想要這樣拍才選擇離開。如今福斯跟迪士尼合併案，ＭＣＵ版的驚奇四超人電影遲早會問世，派頓&middot;瑞德最近不斷公開提到自己當年的計畫，是否在跟迪士尼喊話說要選他呢？各位覺得他會是最適合的人選嗎？"},{"pid":"4f5964e59132ed1ef8afdfdf35676af8f649867b","tid":982943,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"其實拍F4不如話佢地一早已經有超能力上曬外太空到搞科研，Boot嚟boot去好煩，上一版已經垃圾到呢"},{"pid":"41a61215016325f6f66de68fbcf3bb0a50bea930","tid":982943,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"MCU好似未試過一個導演負責兩個系列<br />\n除左羅素兄弟"},{"pid":"0c44eec9772b82cabb321a6a414eed51fe0a1b68","tid":982943,"uid":2545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4f5964e59132ed1ef8afdfdf35676af8f649867b","tid":982943,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"其實拍F4不如話佢地一早已經有超能力上曬外太空到搞科研，Boot嚟boot去好煩，上一版已經垃圾到呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"真係好垃圾...選角好失敗，劇情又好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲衰過Jessica Alba果個series"},{"pid":"a8cf2ce726d84d4fe1f3b3654c934ad267260868","tid":982943,"uid":167426,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好搵呢個導演<br />\n佢套ant man 唔係唔好睇<br />\n但係毫無特色 過目即忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0142dff9873dcef4d36c7504cc754ea40f13a0","tid":982943,"uid":187368,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8cf2ce726d84d4fe1f3b3654c934ad267260868","tid":982943,"uid":167426,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好搵呢個導演<br />\n佢套ant man 唔係唔好睇<br />\n但係毫無特色 過目即忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"Um...個劇本其實唔係佢寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f137f8f89dc36048c044e0d90be01261b4368d65","tid":982943,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f5964e59132ed1ef8afdfdf35676af8f649867b","tid":982943,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"其實拍F4不如話佢地一早已經有超能力上曬外太空到搞科研，Boot嚟boot去好煩，上一版已經垃圾到呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"按MCU處理蜘蛛仔嘅方式<br />\n應該唔會再講起源<br />\n最多用對白輕輕帶過就算<br />\n反正MCU世界觀已經有一大堆超能人<br />\n大家都見怪不怪<br />\n唔使多加解釋"},{"pid":"e13582cc33dc4d9be061415130b43b09bdcda155","tid":982943,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:54:37.000Z","m